Tweets Stocks Analysis Daily/Hourly

Methodology for extraction of Data

For analyzing the effect of tweets with the Stock market, we used Twitter streaming api to capture the monitored stocks in realtime and store them onto a file. The raw data in files was processed using the file twitter-data-cleaner.R. This script can be run incrementally and takes care of merging new data with the already set of processed tweets. The script twitter-data-cleaner.R creates a .Rdata file twitter.RData that has 4 datasets. (TODO add links and information about datasets). There is a script to process the tweets further and calculate the sentimenet score for each tweet ( tweeter-score-compute.R ), It outputes 4 datasets into a file processed-tweets.RData.
